title: Chicken Alfredo casserole
directions: Combine everything from chicken to spinach in a casserole dish.
Cover loosely with foil and bake for 30 minutes. Remove foil, top with mozzarella cheese, and continue to bake for 15 minutes, or until cheese turns golden brown.
Serve with green bean brown rice.
ingredients: 1 pound boneless, skinless chicken breasts, cut into 1-inch strips
